headline: Beyond by RS2 Becomes a Principal Issuing Member of Visa
summary: FRANKFURT, Germany, November 18, 2025--Beyond by RS2, the innovation brand of RS2 Financial Services GmbH, has become a Principal Issuing Member of Visa in Europe – allowing the company to directly issue Visa cards and to launch and manage payment card programs.
